To install the Client Camera Software  Suite in /opt/Client 
follow these steps:

  1. Gaining root privileges and input password:
       sudo su or su root

  2. Change to the directory which contains this INSTALL file, e.g.: 
       cd ~/Client-1.0.0_x86_64

  3. Running the configuration scripts source ./setup.sh

 
  4. Execute /opt/Client/bin/Client.sh to test your cameras.

